  "best_review_details": [
    {
      "text": "These guys have done a fantastic job on our roof. They had patience and communicated clearly with us when giving our quote (very competitive by the way). They also were very timely and did a darn good job of getting this roof on. They were very respectful to my family and they cleaned up after themselves exceptionally well.  They pointed out little things along the way that they went ahead and fix",
      "author": "Hunter",
      "rating": 5,
      "source": "google"
    },
    {
      "text": "If I could add more stars I would! Completely professional from start to finish.\n\nAsh’s expertise is outstanding. We’re delighted with our new roof. Super efficient, we felt completely at ease and took all his expert advice on board.\n\nWe had a new roof in our old house and the A.M.T crew were far superior. Competitive pricing and 100% professional. Amazing communication throughout.\n\nAsh is a total",
      "author": "Mr",
      "rating": 5,
      "source": "google"
    },
    {
      "text": "AMT roofing carried out a complete strip off and re roof of my Victorian age property in Cardiff - 20/10 service and quality from the outset, even with the weather the guys worked solid and made sure everything was clean and tidy after every shift. Also replaced all my guttering / fascia / down pipes to a great standard. Would highly recommend to anyone. Thanks again AMT Roofing",
      "author": "Michael",
      "rating": 5,
      "source": "google"
    }
  ],
